responseText: NSLOCTEXT("[70199B914E7E03A9706A1499CF20B1FD]", "6CBBFAD24C8BA31C43F0F0BF3CCEE083", "Entry #8 We began longer patrols out toward the lush lowlands. Jimmy sustained an injury from a scuffle with some goblins, but should recover quickly thanks to Serval\'s expertise. I think poor Jimmy may feel embarrassed, but while he\'s resting we\'ve nearly finished setting up our camp near the portal. Besides, it was his grand idea to call this place Lionhold, named after our Kaelar roots. I suppose this is what we\'ve been after all along. We have returned home.")
name: CSQ_RVR_0084_FB_MercilessGeneral_Logbook_DLG_3_Response
